
Откажитесь от пользовательского CSS для Bootstrap
Пример кода

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Bootstrap Grid Example</title>
  <!-- Подключение Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center">Bootstrap Grid Example</h1>
    <div class="row">
      <!-- Первый элемент -->
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="card-img-top" alt="Placeholder Image">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Element 1</h5>
            <p class="card-text">This is the first element.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Второй элемент -->
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="card-img-top" alt="Placeholder Image">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Element 2</h5>
            <p class="card-text">This is the second element.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Третий элемент -->
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="card-img-top" alt="Placeholder Image">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Element 3</h5>
            <p class="card-text">This is the third element.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Подключение Bootstrap JS и Popper.js -->
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.3/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
Объяснение
Подключение Bootstrap CSS:


<link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
Контейнер для элементов:


<div class="container mt-5">
  <h1 class="text-center">Bootstrap Grid Example</h1>
  <div class="row">
Первый элемент:


<div class="col-md-4">
  <div class="card">
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="card-img-top" alt="Placeholder Image">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title">Element 1</h5>
      <p class="card-text">This is the first element.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
Второй элемент:


<div class="col-md-4">
  <div class="card">
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="card-img-top" alt="Placeholder Image">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title">Element 2</h5>
      <p class="card-text">This is the second element.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
Третий элемент:


<div class="col-md-4">
  <div class="card">
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="card-img-top" alt="Placeholder Image">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title">Element 3</h5>
      <p class="card-text">This is the third element.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
Подключение Bootstrap JS и Popper.js:


<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.1.3/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
